{"tid":1516562,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鑑古知今:中共60年代三年大饑荒既維穩手法","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T13:32:08.000Z","uid":54303,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"190ade954589765bf0fcffbbe5c093e487279820","tid":1516562,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"原文係殘體, 唔想睇既可以睇我既摘要:<br />\n<a href=\"https://botanwang.com/articles/201404/%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%A5%A5%E8%8D%92%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A4%A7%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbotanwang.com%2Farticles%2F201404%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A5%25A5%25E8%258D%2592%25E6%25B2%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A7%2584%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%2586%259C%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=13864cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://botanwang.com/articles/201404/%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%A5%A5%E8%8D%92%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A4%A7%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0.html</a><br />\n<br />\n原因一: 鼓勵民間互相篤灰, 令人民唔敢講真話, 唔敢信人, 社會凝聚力低就反唔到黨 (由建國開始就做, 60年代民間已無互信無哂靈魂)<br />\n原因二: 中共控制你飯碗, 全國經濟都係由政府嚴密控制<br />\n原因三: 洗腦&amp;訊息控制, 令愚民覺得中共做得好好<br />\n原因四: <span style=\"color: red;\">間唔中搵低下層祭旗, 將所有問題推落佢地到, 中央政府就扮好人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1~3已經做緊, 4中共必定會事後做, 但<span style=\"color: red;\">我地必須要堅持五大訴求, 必須要團結一致, 咁先可以打贏中共呢個專業分化撚</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我地可以點樣反擊?<br />\n1: 個人層面上要保護自己私隱, 最好少用FB (改玩twitter, 唔熟唔好加); 除此之外可以開假FB Account屈番D藍絲轉頭, 咁樣就可以保護自己人<br />\n2. 杯葛所有在港中資, 而且要叫全世界提防中資機構 (尤其電訊/電子/高科技)<br />\n3. 加強對藍絲 &amp;&amp;大陸人既宣傳, 要令佢地清楚知道我地先係主流民意<br />\n4. 勿忘初心, 就算林鄭或者狗狗受到中共清算/義士麻包袋等待遇, <span style=\"color: red;\">請記住我地不分化不篤灰不割席, 直至五大訴求完全達成為止</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8Jw45Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8Jw45Q.png&h=3d106391&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09cae6a1390025111aeaab96903b46d0ca7977f0","tid":1516562,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d85276632b424e5967705f29afaa5650496641","tid":1516562,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93b38138743646edd6d6a11d6a023ac53ab63ab","tid":1516562,"uid":228995,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"無fb 資訊點可以繼續有效一傳十？"},{"pid":"61139e423501a3400bdd1fb2257433f461b62190","tid":1516562,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f898d741cfcd9dbd90f48c10c318cdcb41111f1","tid":1516562,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f93b38138743646edd6d6a11d6a023ac53ab63ab","tid":1516562,"uid":228995,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"無fb 資訊點可以繼續有效一傳十？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"一係你就del哂班藍絲同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用真名政